Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:36.44,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}微笑んだ後ろ姿に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:43.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}泣きそうな顔を隠してた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:49.44,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}優しさで　胸が痛くて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:57.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}こんなに日々が愛しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:03.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}風の音に　夕闇に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:10.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}懐かしい君を思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:16.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「いつまでも　一緒だよ」と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:25.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}叶わぬこと繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:39.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}温もりはこの手に　鮮やかなまま生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:46.91,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}忘れたくないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:59.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}受け取った愛を 未来に変えながら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:36.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個彷彿正在微笑的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:43.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻掩藏著你悲傷的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:49.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的溫柔 讓我心中隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:57.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活居然會如此讓人眷戀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:03.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風聲陣陣 夕陽西斜的黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:10.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想起了讓我思念不已的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:16.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾說「要永遠在一起哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:25.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個承諾卻始終無法兌現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:39.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的溫度 至今還清晰地留在我的手心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:46.91,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想遺忘這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:59.15,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這份愛 在未來某一天將會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被這種低級妖怪附身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我輕舉妄動的話 他的內心有可能會崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}夏目 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到老師的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:01:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該回哪個家來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到處瞎轉悠什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目 難道你迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 就是那個寄養在三世子家的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是還沒記住回家的路呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕 根本沒辦法過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論朝哪邊走…到處都有妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}真想一直住下去啊 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他走回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要再去一次學校嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的都看不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的東西…明明有這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:02:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我好像真的迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再被妖怪追趕的話 我就逃到這裏來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這裏當成秘密基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安安靜靜 誰也不會來打擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.62,biaoti01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(441,370)}遙遠的回家路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼剩下這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好把飯吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼胃口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 三世子 要和貴志一起去學校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小直已經約好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 要多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望有一天可以嘗一嘗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是夏目嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你在和夏目同居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 都住口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不害臊 不害臊 不害臊 不害臊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得向她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒做錯任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我到這個家裏來住…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又剩下這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子 到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那個孩子會來我們家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你睡著前爸爸給你講很多故事好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 你明天要和貴志一起上學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三世子在鬧彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就讓她跟我們一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志一個人沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天破例一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了心會痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們一定很愛我 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再離我遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你家在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說你真正的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的家是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你爸媽住的家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的爸爸和媽媽 你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也不記得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他非常非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 明明記不清了憑什麼還能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你那說法是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸比你爸爸溫柔多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 明明都記不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我去了真正的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能夠…想起更多爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想起很多事 心會痛的更厲害怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是說夏目夫婦的家啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像是從館花先生那裏收到過寫有地址的便條…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你想要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我想要用來做護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 離這裏的不太遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代町的話 沿著城川一直向西走就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 還是個小妖怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？我幫你吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子又把飯剩下了 真是個討厭的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕怕 好怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 走遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能給別人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代町 沿著城川一直向西走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 現在幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會給他們添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷而已 得快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 找到了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐啊 嚇壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志 快進屋去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去和大家道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和三世子兩個人吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意別在意 孩子沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起…對…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼爸媽必須要向大家道歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼爸媽必須被遷怒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做錯事的人明明是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 你給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代町
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著城川…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向西…一直走…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏 有我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我真正的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經空無一人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}爸爸 爸爸 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實 呼喚過很多 很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而每一次 果然都不會有人回應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我怎麼呼喚 怎麼祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究還是會有無法得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒找到回家的路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷了路 精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然怎樣呼喚都得不到回應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我從此再也不會開口了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的 想要遺忘的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我 畫上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這些記憶的碎片組合成了現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使再怎麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我重要的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的記憶也好 心也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部讓我吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心 貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我散去了它的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和蟲子沒什麼兩樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在叫我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到我的記憶了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的記憶才沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們的交情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到我得到友人帳那天為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代町
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著城川一直向西走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我畫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候還挺頑皮的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然畫在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸卻沒有擦掉 都保留下來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起點什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊 幾乎都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多 很多重要的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全都忘光了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽爸爸說 媽媽在這個院子裏的某個地方種了花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也能開花就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能永遠 永遠地開花就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 身體疲憊不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心只想趕快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就沒能吃上那家的烏冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀奇的是 老師竟然沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家 貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了？要走哪邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺應該就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都第三次了啊 沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}檸檬水 檸檬水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地圖不是你畫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人 我們先走一步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}檸檬水 檸檬水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會…是這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超好聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜田！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們總算來了 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊！你們居然捷足先登啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是好好調查之後才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽夏目同學說你們今天來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等著呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會涌出檸檬水 說的是這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊！通紅通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 因為生銹了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要運氣不是太差 是喝不壞肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 西村 從你開始喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳 猜拳決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有悲傷的日子 也有痛苦的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 今後也許還會遇到這樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 貴志 再靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑 笑一笑 貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 有沒有照好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是~可樂餅版的~布魯斯哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋叔叔 塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 能再照一張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓五郎 要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些如寶物一般珍貴的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\c&H0000A9&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\pos(247,355)}完結。
